comment:
* Captures the skin temperature of a user. Each record can represent a series of measurements of
 * temperature differences.

variables.name: SKIN_TEMPERATURE_DELTA_AVG
variables.comment:
* Metric identifier to retrieve average skin temperature delta using aggregate APIs in {@link
     * HealthConnectManager}.

variables.name: SKIN_TEMPERATURE_DELTA_MIN
variables.comment:
* Metric identifier to retrieve minimum skin temperature delta using aggregate APIs in {@link
     * HealthConnectManager}.

variables.name: SKIN_TEMPERATURE_DELTA_MAX
variables.comment:
* Metric identifier to retrieve maximum skin temperature delta using aggregate APIs in {@link
     * HealthConnectManager}.

variables.name: VALID_MEASUREMENT_LOCATIONS
variables.comment:
* Valid set of values for this IntDef. Update this set when add new type or deprecate existing
     * type.
     *
     * @hide

methods.name: public Temperature getBaseline()
methods.comment: * @return baseline skin temperature in {@link Temperature} unit.

methods.name: public List<Delta> getDeltas()
methods.comment: * @return an unmodified list of skin temperature deltas in {@link TemperatureDelta} unit.

methods.name: public boolean equals(@Nullable Object object)
methods.comment:
* Indicates whether some other object is "equal to" this one.
     *
     * @param object the reference object with which to compare.
     * @return {@code true} if this object is the same as the object.

methods.name: public int hashCode()
methods.comment: * @return a hash code value for the object.
